OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe heatwave continues today
OL,6,Fwith dry weather and hot sunshine.
OL,7,FFeeling hot in the strong sunshine
OL,8,Fwith high UV levels, but less hot than
OL,9,FFriday. A more notable breeze will
OL,10,Fdevelop through the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining dry this evening
OL,13,Fwith plenty of late evening sunshine.
OL,14,FA few mist patches are possible, but
OL,15,Fclear for most. Staying warm overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FAny mist quickly lifting and
OL,18,Fclearing giving another very warm and
OL,19,Fsunny day with a brisk breeze across
OL,20,Fthe region.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
