OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FRemaining very warm, dry and sunny in
OL,7,Fthe outlook, although an easterly
OL,8,Fbreeze will bring a little relief to
OL,9,Fthe hot conditions.
